<tr>
<td><a href="/scp-2144">SCP-2144</a></td>
<td><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/schrodingers-kitty" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2137696); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2137696&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869514" alt="Schrodingers_Kitty" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2137696)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/schrodingers-kitty" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2137696); return false;">Schrodingers_Kitty</a></span></td>
<td>Misconception of a Brainchild</td>
<td>It's a literal Schrodinger's Cat and is an exercise in deconstructing a literalist take on the famous thought experiment and how a flawed idea survives in the &quot;real&quot; world.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/scp-1186">SCP-1186</a></td>
<td><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bunton" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225550); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1225550&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869514" alt="Bunton" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1225550)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bunton" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1225550); return false;">Bunton</a></span></td>
<td>Cochlear Cicadas</td>
<td>I looked at the original version, and thought to myself <em>Journey to the West</em> and Xuanzang (a.k.a. the Golden Cicada). And it gave me the direction to press for rewrite.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/scp-2247">SCP-2247</a></td>
<td><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timmytim" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2617518); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2617518&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869514" alt="TimmyTim" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2617518)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timmytim" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2617518); return false;">TimmyTim</a></span></td>
<td>&quot;What did I go through to seek a new employer?&quot;</td>
<td>When it comes to anomalous humans, the usual question is &quot;How did they adapt from life as a normal human?&quot; Now, what if it is reversed, that an object become human instead?</td>
</tr>
</table>
