<td><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agatharights" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(232934); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=232934&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869514" alt="agatharights" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=232934)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agatharights" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(232934); return false;">agatharights</a></span></td>
<td><strong>Subject:</strong> Dr. Hu An</td>
<td>It was something based on my own feelings towards Chinese New Year. Despite it being billed as a time where families get together, modern trends suggest otherwise. That said, the ideal remains as something some people desire in the hectic-ness of daily life.</td>
</tr>
